'''Roger Barton''' was an editor for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. His son, [[Aidan Barton|Aidan]], portrayed infant [[Luke Skywalker|Luke]] and [[Leia Skywalker Organa Solo|Leia]] in ''Revenge of the Sith'': When it was time to shoot close-ups of the infant Luke and Leia, the older Barton revealed that he had just had a baby and suggested that they used his son for the scenes.<ref name="Looper">{{WebCite|url=https://www.looper.com/828214/revenge-of-the-siths-baby-luke-and-leia-actor-aidan-barton-talks-star-wars-and-mark-hamill-exclusive-interview|text=Revenge Of The Sith's Baby Luke And Leia Actor Aidan Barton Talks Star Wars And Mark Hamill - Exclusive Interview|author=Harbet, Xandra|date=April 11, 2022|archivedate=20220418144853}}</ref>

